    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but even if i stop trying, nothing changes. i'm still just... there. stuck in this loop of feeling like an outsider looking in. it feels like there's no point in pushing through the exhaustion if the destination is always the same. it just feels like a waste of energy.",
