    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's what i mean... even \"small acts\" take energy i don't have. it's like i'm just stuck in a world that wasn't built for me, and the more i try to force it, the more it hurts. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually find peace or stop this noise is to just not be around anymore. is that even a rational thought to have?",
